\mt1 PAS NAMBA WAN YOHANE MENI GAENUA  
\ip \it Yohane meni susu eto ego emira pas ei awa gaenua. Zo awa ego ewa: Nuai me ewanana puro nuai amira susu kerenamu sero gaenua. Nakai Anutu ata Yesu Kristo amire dubara dumi pupinoise otao mamai nasokai amire dai dubara dumi pumanisekai senua. Zo awa ego ewa: Opi sai ema eni meni kei awero Tuara ge ninai ema amira duba sisinoise ego toisowa awa, “Tama aiso awa nena waya. Awa pasinara masi awa. Are Yesu meni tama aisora kaka kei awamu. Nu ema meni nuago inoisonua, ata nu tama aiso tepo. Nu Anutura Mai me oko aewa.” Opi sai ema ago toisowa, are Yohane meni opi nusokare puro osamu sero pas ei awa gaenua.\it*  
\c 1  
\s1 Nuai me ewanana amira Mama.  
\p
\v 1 Nuai me ewanana amira Mama* nu susura ena tupise noisonua amira ge kereniro nikare tugata inowenakare awa. Nakare ge nuso dana meni nininakare. Nakare nu giti moka nasokare meni ginakare. Nakare nu giro baitinakare. Nakare nu wana meni ziro ginakare.  
\v 2 Nuai me ewananara Mama kei damu ninu ginakare awa. Nuai me ewananara Mama nu ami Mamera nana ena muro nasokare nana ena kei damu ninua. Are nuaira Mama awa nimorekare kereniro tugata inowenakare.  
\v 3 Awa nena ginakare o ge nininakare da awa nikare tugata inowenakare awa. Tugata wanakare tairo nuai nasokai kei awai daimata wero nuamukai sero towenakare awa. Tairo nuai nasokai awa Mamato Mai Yesu Kristore dai tairo nowenakai awa.  
\v 4 Yawa sara wai nasokai kei awero baitaise pas ei awa nimorekare gainona ewa.   
\s1 Zasimaira noise pasina oko bezero puro nuanekai.  
\p
\v 5 Ge bowi Yesura nana ena ego nininakare, are nikare tugata inowenakare awa. Anutu nu zasimai gege. Mume zo nuso nana oko itia.  
\v 6 Nakai mumera noise “Na Anutura nana desenitinona” asamunonakai, awa opi wamunoya. Ago inoise ge me oko puro nuamunonakai.  
\v 7 Ata Anutu nu nutope zasimaira nowia da ago ine nakai zasimaira nuamunonakai, awa dara tairo otao kokopai wamunonakai. Ago wanakai Mai nuso Yesu Kristora orara meni asina nasokai dapikarago sewai saramuro nuamunonakai awa.  
\v 8 Nakai pasina tepo asamunonakai, awa duba nasokai etete namunonakai. Ago wanakai duba nasokaira ge me oko itamunoya.  
\v 9 Anutu nu saramai gege. Ata nakai pasina disaise nu tuma dianakai te wamunoya. Are pasina nasokai kerenamunonakai, awa nu pasina nasokai disero waya nasokai dapikarago sewai saramamunonakai awa.  
\v 10 “Nakai pasina kaka wamu nowenakai,” ago samunonakai, awa nakai Anutu opi sai ema asamunonakai. Ago wanakai ge nuso duba nasokaira oko itamunoya.   
\s1 Kristo nu sogawai nasokai.  
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 Mai mamai naso, nikare pasina wai azu, ge ei awa nimorekare gainona. Ata zo nu pasina zo wamunoya, ami ego gaiseyo: Sogawai nasokai Mamera nana benaura itise nakai soga inowia. Soga wai awa Yesu Kristo awa. Nu ema saramai.  
\v 2 Nu ami Anutu uzutamu pasina nasokaira ina betenua. Agoro pasina nasokai gege kota, zebu sero ema dapikarago amira pasina dimunua.  
\v 3 Are nakai potai ge nuso dimamunonakai, awa nu giro baititinowenakai awa gamunonakai.  
\v 4 Ata zo nu potai ge nuso kaka dimamu inoise “Na Anutu gai” asamunoya, awa nu opi sai ema wamunoya. Ema ago ine awa ge me meni duba nusora oko itia.  
\v 5-6 Zo nu Anutura ge niniro dimamunoya ami Anutu ara tapinowia. “Nakai Anutura nana deseniro nowenakai” asinowenakai ami Yesu noisonua ago ine te nuanekai. Ago wamunonakai, awa nakai Anutura nana me deseniro nowenikaita tepo ni, amira susu gamunonakai.   
\s1 Zasimaira noise otaore dubara dumi pumai awa potai ge seka.  
\p
\v 7 Otao mamai naso, na potai ge seka zo oko nimorekare gainona. Awa matu, Yesura ge niniwa amira ana niniro tupewewa awa. Oziga ge niniwa awa potai ge matu awa.  
\v 8 Noko ge gainona awa potai ge seka inoya. Ge awa Yesura nana ata nisokare nana dai me inoya. Amira susu ego ewa. Mume dainitinoi zasimai me meni kei damu niro zasipitinoya.  
\v 9 Are zo nu otao nuso iwo inowia ami “Na zasimaira nona,” asamunoya, ata nu mumera nuai gege nowia.  
\v 10 Ota zo nu otao nusore dubara dumi pupinowia ami zasimaira nowia. Ago inowia ami pasinara wawa amira kawa nuso nana oko itia.  
\v 11 Ata zo nu otao nuso iwo inowia ami mumera itewia. Nu mumera noise nu nago nago susawi awa oko gosinowia. Nera kota, mume meni giti moka nuso azenu giti guma wago wenu nowia.   
\p
\v 12 O mai mamai naso, Anutu meni pasina nisokare Yesu emo disenua, are ge nimorekare gainona.  
\v 13 O mamana, nikare nu nuai gege noisonua nowia awa giro baititinowewa, are ge nimorekare gainona. O mai seka, nikare wayara mama awa puro osewa, are ge nimorekare gainona. O mai mamai, nikare Mama giro baititinowewa, are nimorekare ge gainona.  
\v 14 O mamana, nikare nu nuai gege noisonua nowia amira susu giro baititinowewa, are ge nimorekare gainona. O mai seka, nikare putou nisokare itia, o Anutura ge duba nisokarera itia, o wayara mama puro osewa, are nimorekare ge gainona awa.   
\s1 Duba nasokai zebura nenara oko itaise.  
\p
\v 15 Duba nisokare zeburata zebura nenara oko potawe. Zo nu duba nuso zebura nenara potamunoya ami duba nuso Mamera nana oko potamunoya.  
\v 16 Zebura nena dapikarago — tama meni duba-duba wai, o giti moka meni giro duba-duba wai, o wau emo tama puro witai — kotumai awa Mamera oko aewa. Kotumai awa zebura gege awa.  
\v 17 Ota zebu awa sisamunoya, o zebura nena emo duba-duba inowera nukare awa dai sisamunora. Ata zo nu Anutura ge niniro dimamunoya ami nuai gege nuamunoya.   
\s1 Kristora iwo kei awero itia.  
\p
\v 18 Mai awiso naso, zebura be tepo inoya. Kristora iwo mamunoya awa nikare ninisewa, ata Kristora iwo dainiro emoko kei awero nowera, are zebura be tepo inoya, awa gosinonakai.  
\v 19 Nukare dubu nasokai nana soe ena kei awero bamuwa, ata nukare otao mamai nasokai me wero nuai awa oko noisowa. Nukare otao mamai nasokai me wero nuamera sia, awa nakai oko duamera. Nakai dowa, amira susu nusokare ego ine gosinonakai. Namorekai dai noe dowa ami otao mamai nasokai me oko aewa.  
\v 20 Ota ninekare meni awa Yesu meni Ozana iyetinu osenu puro nowewa, are nikare dapikarago ge me gosinowa awa.  
\v 21 Nikare ge me sirinowewita asero pas ei awa oko gainona. Tepo awa. Nikare ge me ninitinowewa, are ge nimorekare gainona awa. Opi ge dapikarago awa ge mera nana mokara ena oko kei awinowia, awa gosinowa.   
\s1 Anutu Mamato Maire oko zaumanekai.  
\p
\v 22 Opi sai ema awa are samunowi? Zo nu “Yesu awa Kristo me oko aewa,” ago samunoya, awa nu opi sai ema ago sewo. Nu awa Kristora iwo bamu inoya awa. Nu Mamato Maire begi inoya.  
\v 23 Zo nu Mai begi wamunoya ami Mama dai begi wamunoya awa. Ata zo nu Mai tuma diamunoya ami Mamere dai nuamunoya.  
\v 24 Ata nikare ge susura ena niniro tupisowa awa poti dube niro noiwo. Poti dube niro nuamunowa, awa Maito Mamere nimorekare dai nuamunorato.  
\v 25 Yesu meni namorekai ego seroninua awa, “Na nuai me ewanana nimorekare potamunona.”   
\s1 Ozana meni ge me namorekai gipinowia.  
\p
\v 26 Nikare etete namu tora amira susu gawise ego gainona ewa.  
\v 27 Yesu meni Ozana iyetinu osenu pumuwa nisokare nana itewia. Are ema zo nikare gipaise oko sawe. Tepo awa. Ozana pumuwa ami ge dapikarago nimorekare tugata-magata inowia. Ge awa opi tepo, awa me. Are ebata Ozana meni gipenua da awa patitinoise Yesure dai noiwo.   
\p
\v 28 Mai awiso naso, nikare Yesure dai noiwo. Nu kei awai amire nakai benau nusora ena me niro nu tema wai tepo zewai wero dopamukai sero zeme numore dai noiwo.  
\v 29 Anutu nu etutiro nowia, nikare ago ninitinowewa, are ema zo da ago etutiro nuai giro ego sewo, “Nu Anutura nana ena kei awai awa.”   
\s1 Anutura mai awiso nonakai amira susu.  
\c 3  
\p
\v 1 Mamera dubara dumi pai bamubake awa giwo. Nu dubara dumi namorekai bamubake pupinoise mai matere bamere nuso asinowia awa. Are ago wero nowenakai awa. Ema Tuara ge tepo nowera ami Anutu oko gosinora, are nukare susu nasokai oko giro baititinowera.  
\v 2 Otao mamai naso, nakai zeme emire Anutura mai wero nowenakai. Ata noma nogo ine wamunonikai, awa zeme kaka kei damu namu. Ata ego gosinonakai: Kristo kei awai amire nakai benau nuso giro nu ine wamunonakai.  
\v 3 Are zo nu kei awaira be nuso dia inoise nuamunoya ami Tua nu saramai nowia da ago ine nuamu sero giro duba nuso sewinoise nuamunoya.   
\s1 Pasina wero Satanra mai wamunora.  
\p
\v 4 Zo nu pasina inowia ami Anutura potai ge awa dainitinoise nowia. Pasina wai awa potai ge dainai awa.  
\v 5 Are Yesure ego ninitinowewa awa: Nu pasina disamu sero kei awenua, noko nu pasina tepo noisonua awa.  
\v 6 Zo nu Yesure dai nowia ami pasina inoise oko nowia. Ata zo nu pasina inowia ami Yesura susu oko gosinowia.  
\v 7 Mai awiso naso, zo meni duba nisokare sisamu sai oko ninawe. Yesu nu saramai gege. Da ago ine zo nu etutiro nowia ami ema saramai wero nowia.  
\v 8 Ota zo nu pasina inowia ami Satanra ema wero nowia. Satan nu pasina susura ena inoisonua inoise nowia. Anutura Mai meni Satanra bua sisero tepo wamu sero kei awenua.   
\s1 Anutura mai wero noise pasina inoise nuai ine tepo.  
\p
\v 9 Zo nu Anutura nana ena kei awero nowia ami pasina inoise oko nowia. Nera kota, Anutura nuai nuso nana itia. Nu Anutura nana ena kei awenua, are pasina inoise oko nuamunoya.  
\v 10 Are Anutura mai awisota Satanra mai awiso ni, amira susu nusokare awa ego ine kei awai gamunowa. Zo nu etutiro kaka nuamu wamunoya, awa nu Anutura mai ago oko samunowa. O zo nu otao nusore dubara dumi kaka pamu wamunoya, awa numore da ago ine samunowa.  
\v 11 Tuara ge susura ena niniro tupewewa awa ego ine ewa: Dubara dumi ina-pa wanekai.  
\v 12 Ota Kainra ebata oko patanekai. Nu Satanra mai wero nami nuso denu betenua. Awa nogoro denu betenu? Awa ego emira. Nu nuai nuso waya, ata nami nusora nuai awa kokopai, are nu nami nuso denu betenua awa.   
\s1 Yesu meni namorekai dubara dumi pumunua, are da ago wanekai.  
\p
\v 13 Otao mamai naso, ema Yesu kaka tuma diamu inowera ami nikare iwo wara giro oko di tainawe.  
\v 14 Nakai otao mamai nasokaire dubara dumi pupinowenakai, are nakai natopekai ego gosinowenakai: Nakai ema ititi tepo meni nuago wai amira tani awa doro nuai me topetinakai awa. Ata zo nu dubara dumi kaka pumamu inowia ami ititi tepo meni nuago inowia.  
\v 15 Zo nu otao nuso iwo wamunoya, awa nu mai dai betai ema awa. Agoro nikare mai dai betai ema amira susu gosinowewa. Nuai me ewanana awa nusokare nana oko itia.  
\v 16 Yesu nu nakai emo nuai nuso donua, are dubara dumi pumaira susu ginakai awa. Are nakai da ago ine otao mamai nasokai emo nuai nasokai duanisekai sai awa.  
\v 17 Ema zo nu zebura wau moni zamai bamubake nuso nana itai amire otao nuso bogamasa nuai giro gago-giago wero dagia wamunoya, awa numore ego sewo, “Nu Anutu oko ara tapinowia.”  
\v 18 Mai awiso naso, nakai dumi pai awa be meni daba kota, wana meni o duba meni dumi me panekai.   
\s1 Anutura benaura azu tepo nuanekai.  
\p
\v 19 Ago werokai Tuara ge me amira dubu wero nowenikaita awa gamunonakai awa. Are duba nasokai meni nakai gera potamu awita sai nakai Anutura nana giti mokara duba uzutanekai.  
\v 20 Nera kota, nakai ego gosinonakai. Anutura kotumai meni kotumai nakai dainai. Nu nena bamubamu dapikarago amira susu gosinowia.  
\v 21 Otao mamai naso, duba nasokai meni nakai gera potamu awita kaka samu wai Anutura benaura azu tepo zewai wero nuamunonakai.  
\v 22 Agoro nakai potai ge nuso dipinoise nena wawenakai giti moka nusora kokopai inowia, are nena zota zo emo begomo sawenakai potitinowia.  
\v 23 Potai ge nuso awa ego itia ewa: Mai nuso Yesu Kristo tuma didinoise duba meni dumi ina-pa wanekai. Ago wanisekai senua awa.  
\v 24 Zo nu potai ge nuso dipinowia ami Anuture dai nuawi Anutu numore dai nowia. Anuture duba da inowenakai awa Ozana potinua ami namorekai kerenawi gosinowenakai awa.   
\s1 Ozana susu giti nora.  
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 Otao mamai naso, porofete opi dainiro zebura kei awero nowera, are ema dapikarago “Anutura Ozana naso nana itia,” ago towera amira ge ninawa me oko wae. Ozana nusokare Anutura nana ena maita asero nukare gaero gamu wewo.  
\v 2 Anutura Ozana ego awa gamunowa: Zo nu “Yesu Kristo ema wero kei awenua,” awa ziro tata-tata wamunoya ami Ozana Anutura nana ena mai awa puro noya, ago gamunowa.  
\v 3 Ata zo nu “Yesu ema wero kei awenua,” awa kaka ziro tata-tata wamu wamunoya ami Ozana Anutura nana ena mai awa oko puro noya, ago gamunowa. Nu ozana ewe puro nowia. Ozana ewe awa Kristora iwo bamubake amira nana ena mai. Gita ge nuso niniwa; nu zebura kei awaise sai. Are nu awa emoko zebura kei awero nowia.  
\v 4 Mai awiso naso, nikare Anutura mai awiso, are porofete opi awa puro osewa. Ago wewa, nera kota, Anutura Ozana amira putou awa ewe, o ema Yesu tuma kaka diamu nowera amira ozanara putou awa ewe. Are Anutura Ozana amira putou meni ozana nusokarera putou dainitinowia.  
\v 5 Porofete opi awa nukare zebura gege. Are zebura ge gege towera. Ago sawera zebura ema meni dana zaawero ninitinowera awa.  
\v 6 Nanekai meni awa Anutura, are zo nu Anutu gosinowia ami ge nasokai ninitinowia. Ota Anutura nana ena kaka kei awamu ami ge nasokai azu towera. Nukare ago wawera ge mera Ozanare opi saira ozanare amira susu kei awawi gosinowenakai awa.   
\s1 Anutu nu dubara dumi pumai amira mama.  
\p
\v 7 Otao mamai naso, nakai dubara dumi ina-pa wanekai. Nera kota, dubara dumi pai awa Anutura nana ena tupewia. Are zo nu dubara dumi pupinowia ami Anutura mai wero nowia. Nu Anutu giro baititinowia.  
\v 8 Ata zo nu dubara dumi kaka pumamu inowia ami Anutu oko gosinowia. Nera kota, Anutu nu dubara dumi pumai amira mama.  
\v 9 Anutu meni Mai nuso daimata awa namorekai nuai tamaise iyetinu ose zebura ninua. Amira ana dubara dumi pumai nuso namorekai potinu kei damu ninua awa.  
\v 10 Dubara dumi pumaira susu ego ine itia. Nakai Anuture dubara dumi oko pumunakai. Tepo awa. Nune nakai emo dubara dumi pupinoise Mai nuso iyetinu osero pasina nasokaira ina betenua.   
\s1 Anutura dubara dumi gosinoise da ago ine wanekai.  
\p
\v 11 Otao mamai naso, Anutu nu namorekai dubara dumi bamubake pumunua, are nakai da ago ine dubara dumi ina-pa inoise nuanekai.  
\v 12 Zo meni Anutu giti moka nuso meni oko ginua. Ata duba meni dumi ina-pa wamunonakai, awa Anutu nasokai nana nuamunoya. Ago nuai dubara dumi nuso meni nasokai nana kei awero baitamunoya awa.  
\v 13 Nu Ozana nuso namorekai potinua, are ego gosinowenakai. Nu namorekai dai nowia, da ago ine nakai numore dai nowenakai.  
\v 14 Mama nu Mai nuso zebu serora ema nakai wayara ena soyaise iyetinu osenua, awa giti moka nasokare me meni ginakare, are ge awa sero kerenitinowenakare awa.  
\v 15 Are ema zo meni “Yesu nu Anutura Mai me” asero ziro tata-tata wamunoya nu ami Anuture tairo nuamunoya. Ago wai Anutu da ago ine numore tairo nuamunoya awa.  
\v 16 Anutura dubara dumi nasokai nana kei awenua awa ginakai me wenua.  
\p Anutu nu dubara dumi pumai amira mama, are zo nu dubara dumire nuamunoya, awa nu ami Anuture dai tairo nuamunoya. Ago wai Anutu numore dai tairo nuamunoya awa.  
\v 17 Zebura nuai nasokai awa Yesura nuai ine, are Anutu meni erama awina-dawina inoise ina potamunoya be amire nakai kotora kei awero azu tepo zewai wero dopanisekai dubara dumi nusora me awa nasokai nana te kei awenua.  
\v 18 Azu waito dubara dumire nuto dara tairo itai ine tepo. Dubara dumi bamubake meni azu wai awa musunitinowia. Azu waira susu ego ewa. Zo nu pasina nusora ina pai azu inowia ami yaya tapinowia. Ema Anutu azu inowera amira nana dubara dumi pumai nuso amira me awa kaka kei awero baitamu inowia, are nukare nu azu inowera.  
\v 19 Anutu meni gita namorekai dubara dumi pumunua, are nakai dubara dumire dai nowenakai awa.  
\v 20 Zo nu “Anuture dubara dumi pupinowena,” asinoise otao nuso iwo inowia ami opi sai ema wero nowia. Zo nu otao nuso giti moka meni gosinowia awa iwo wamunoya ami Anutu giti moka meni kaka gamu inowia amire dubara dumi pai ine tepo awa.  
\v 21 Yesura potai ge ego nasokai nana itia awa: Zo nu Anuture dubara dumi pupinowia ami otao nusore dubara dumi dai paise.   
\s1 Tuma diaire meni zebura etetenai puro osamunoya.  
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Ema zo meni “Yesu nu Kristo” asinoise tuma diamunoya nu ami Anutura nana ena kei awenua asamunowa awa. Zo nu Mamere dubara dumi pamunoya ami da ago awiso nusore pamunoya awa.  
\v 2 Nakai Anutura mai awisore dubara dumi pupinowenikaita tepo ni? Awa Anuture dubara dumi pupinoise potai ge nuso awa dimanakai ami kerenamunoya.  
\v 3 Anuture dubara dumi pumai amira susu awa ego ewa. Nakai potai ge nuso dipinoise nuanekai. Potai ge nuso awa mou tepo awa.  
\v 4 Anutura mai awiso dapikarago ami zebura tani puro osisinowera. Putou nemi zebura tani puro osisinowi? Tuma diai nasokaira putou meni zebura tani puro osisinowia.   
\s1 Anutu meni Yesura susu kereninua.  
\p
\v 5 Ai meni putoure wero zebura tani dapikarago puro osamunoi? Zo nu “Yesu awa Anutura Mai” ago toise tuma diamunoya ami ago wamunoya awa.  
\v 6 Yesu Kristo nu ou gutaire orara ni pasinaira tetaire dai kei awenua awa. Oure gege kota, oure orarare dai kei awenua awa. Ozana meni Yesura susu kerenitinowia. Nera kota, Ozana nu ge me susure amira mama.  
\v 7-8 Are nena etorobara — Ozana ata ou ata orara — ami poti dara niro susu daimata ei awa kerenitinowera: Yesu nu Anutura Mai.  
\v 9 Ema meni poti dara niro sawera gawenakai me inowia awa. Are Anutu meni ge nuso soga wawi me gege inowia awa. Ge me nuso meni eramara ge me dainitinowia. Are nu ge me toise Mai nusora susu poti damu ninua.  
\v 10 Zo nu Anutura Mai tuma diamunoya amira nana dubara Anutura ge me itamunoya. Zo nu ge Anutu meni Mai nuso soga inoise senua awa gai me amu wamunoya ami Anuture opi sai ema asamunoya.  
\v 11 Susu kereninua awa ego ine itia. Anutu nu nuai me ewanana namorekai potinua. Nuai me ewananara mama awa Mai nuso.  
\v 12 Are zo nu Mai nusore dara tairo nuamunoya ami nuai me ewanana pumamunoya. Ota zo nu Anutura Maire dara kaka tayamu wamunoya ami nuai me ewanana oko pumamunoya.   
\p
\v 13 Nikare Anutura Mai tuma didinowewa ami ego ninawise sero ge ei awa gainona awa: Nikare nuai me ewanana puro nowewa. Awa gawise sero gainona.  
\v 14 Nakai ego gosinowenakai: Nakai Anutura ara tamai awa tamuro amire begomo samunonakai, awa nu ninamunoya. Are begomo samu sero azu inoise kota, zewai wero nuso nana tupewenakai.   
\p
\v 15 Nena zota zo emo begomo sanakai ninamunoya, awa gosinowenakai. Are nena emo nu begomo towenakai awa potitinowia, awa dai gosinowenakai.  
\v 16 Zo nu otao nuso meni pasina wai gamunoya, pasina awa so wayara bayai amira kota, pasina peu zo wai giro nu emo begomo saise. Begomo sai Anutu meni nuai otao nusore potamunoya. Pasina so wayara gegenai amire kota, pasina peure tona. Pasina mou- mau so wayara gegenai awa itia. Pasina ago ine emo begomo sawise oko tona.  
\v 17 Nuai waya dapikarago awa pasina gege. Ota pasina eni awa so wayara gegenai oko inoya.   
\p
\v 18 Nakai ego gosinowenakai: Anutura nana ena kei awai meni pasina oko inowera. Anutura Mai meni gosinoise dia inowia, are pasinara mama meni nukare waya wai ine oko itia.   
\p
\v 19 Nakai ego gosinowenakai: Nakai Anutura nana ena kei awai, ata Tuara ge tepo nowera nukare awa pasinara mama amira putoura nowera.   
\p
\v 20 Nakai ego gosinowenakai: Anutura Mai meni osero kotumai namorekai potinua, are nakai Anutu me giro baititinowenakai. Nakai Anutura Mai Yesu Kristo amire dai nowenakai, are nakai Anutu me amire dai nowenakai. Nu awa Anutu me. Nu nuai me ewananara mama awa.  
\v 21 Mai awiso naso, tua opi sai ami emo uma wewo.   